Planning 

Aim:

-Design cali storage system for songs released by an artist/group

-Records saved in a JSON file

Stage 1:
Create server
Create client
Create database
Create protocol buffer

Stage 2:
Implement interface in client:
Interface enable user to:
Write record
Update record
Read record

Stage 3:
