-if false{
save file
}

else {
return (key)* and latest version
}

Stage 4:
Update record function:
-Client capable of sending details attached to record (supposed to be key, version and
-If details unknown{
return error message
}
-Else {save modified, replaced with new version}
-When update is successful return key and new version
